                                               <title>Tables of the names and descriptions of the prophets, illustrations of the Ka'ab and the Prophet's tomb at Medina, and ornamental designs built around Muhammad's staff, sandals, etc.</title>
                                               <textLang mainLang="tr">Turkish</textLang></msItem>
                                          <msItem xml:id="manuscript_14540-item1.9"><locus from="139b" to="157b">139b-157b</locus>
